      "rationale": "Linear elastic constitutive model applied to Ti-6Al-4V ELI screw and rod (E = 114 GPa, ν = 0.33) and UHMWPE test blocks (E = 0.9 GPa, ν = 0.4). Model form selection justified by the quasi-static loading regime and the observation that yield occurs at the screw-rod interface, not within the bulk material. Frictional contact (μ = 0.2) applied at screw-rod interface and screw-block interfaces. Model form validated against N=11 experimental load-displacement curves; residuals are normally distributed (Shapiro-Wilk p = 0.31) with no systematic bias. Gradation 3 achieved: model form selection documented with physics justification and validated against experimental data with statistical residual analysis.",
